  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in the bottom of a tagine or Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add chicken and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add curry paste and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add broth, coconut milk, honey, fish sauce, hot sauce, salt, and pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring to a boil, then cover and transfer to oven.",
    "Bake at 375°F for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in lemon juice and continue to bake for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot."
  ],
